‚úÖ 9. Focus Indicators (‚è±Ô∏è 3 min)
File: 
Home.css

Aggiungi alla fine:

css
/* ===== ACCESSIBILITY - FOCUS INDICATORS ===== */
a:focus,
button:focus,
input:focus {
    outline: 3px solid #FFD700;
    outline-offset: 2px;
}
.hero-btn:focus {
    outline: 3px solid #FFD700;
    outline-offset: 3px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
}
#side-bar a:focus {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    outline: 3px solid #FFD700;
    outline-offset: -3px;
}
/* Focus solo tastiera (non mouse) */
*:focus:not(:focus-visible) {
    outline: none;
}
*:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid #FFD700;
    outline-offset: 2px;
}
